>
  <p>One of the questions I hear most is: "How do I know if I need therapy?" And there's a simple answer: if the question is already on your mind, it's probably a good time to explore it.</p>
  <p>You don't need to be in crisis. You don't need to hit rock bottom. Therapy isn't only for emotional emergencies — it's also a space for growth, self-knowledge, and fine-tuning your inner compass.</p>
